       int ev_block()

DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       After a process has opened an event queue with ev_init and
       ev_open, ev_block causes the process to sleep until  there
       is an event in the event queue.

RReettuurrnn vvaalluueess
       A call to ev_block returns -1 if the process does not have
       an open event queue, or if it is interrupted.  It  returns
       zero if it succeeds.

